data.description: 3 bedroom Bungalow on a quiet street. Home offers a  2 year old roof with new gutters, 3 1/2 year old Tankless Water Heater and a Brand new furnace installed in December 2023.  Located on a culdesac street.  Plenty of space for a garage. 2 bedrooms down and one possible 3rd up.  All Mechanicals are up to date.  Refrigerator and washer and dryer included.  New storage shed in backyard for lawn equipment.  Back yard is fenced.  Home needs some cosmetic updating.  Close to shopping, and schools.
